articles.title: India vs Australia 3rd T20I playing XI tip off: Gaikwad-Jaiswal to continue as openers, Avesh to replace Arshdeep and, Head to return for AUS - The Indian Express
articles.description: With India having gained a 2-0 lead and Australia on the verge of a five-match series defeat, both the teams are expected to make changes to their lineups in Guwahati.
articles.content: Having gained a 2-0 lead with wins in Vishakhapatnam and Thiruvananthapuram, India will be looking to sweep the five-match T20I series against Australia in Guwahati. Led by Suryakumar Yadav, the men … [+2836 chars]
